      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Prepare and validate raw mass spectrometry data (feature quantification tables and MS/MS spectra) for taxonomically informed metabolite annotation by converting to standardized formats (CSV/TSV and MGF) and verifying structural integrity before downstream analysis.",
